  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This pilot project strengthens the supervision and monitoring activities of the national tuberculosis (TB) control strategy through the establishment of a Short Message System (SMS) for patient monitoring referred to as &quot;mTB.&quot; The project is designed to break the chain of transmission of both regular and multi-drug-resistance TB, ensure patient treatment compliance, reduce the number of cases who abandon treatment, monitor adverse effects, and monitor the administration of medications.</narrative>
  </description>
